### Our Strategic Approach

**Differentiation:** We own the almond-specific angle — every colour recommendation ties back to *why it works on an almond shape* (elongating effect, pointed tip geometry, how the tapered shape interacts with sheer vs opaque finishes). Competitors give generic skin-tone guides; we give almond-nail-specific skin-tone guides. We also weave in 2026's dominant colour stories (earthy neutrals, milky sheers, chocolate browns, cherry reds, sage greens, dusty mauves) rather than listing timeless shades only.

